Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.19,0:01:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在背后撞我车子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑 那不是你的错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没想到前面在跑的家伙技术那么差
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没预料会有人用这么慢的速度入弯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.55,0:01:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没来得及踩Brake就撞上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 池谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要我道歉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按我们的规则进行一次比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赢了的话 我就诚心诚意地向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的规则 是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们叫做胶布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Speed Stars不是有下坡第一人的86吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我转告那个86小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下星期六晚十点 我在这等他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了 Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事 是要向拓海挑战吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他好像不认识拓海的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 应战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match还是什么都好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那种家伙打败 让他跪下道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要开玩笑了 太危险了 树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不能扭尽轪盘的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是池谷前辈 拓海连FD和32都能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上点规则也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方肯定在这种条件下作了很多练级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 这么乱来的比赛 绝对不要接受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点点比赛的意思都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用理这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？胶布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样太危险了 那么拓海的意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是平常的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是冷静还是不会被激怒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来没有兴趣比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想要拓海去跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那个浑蛋打败让他下跪 这样才够痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方又是我们Levin和APEX的宿命车型Civil
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们年轻时也有设置规则或限制来做各种比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而胶布Death Match是最危险的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match就真的那么危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒没怎么感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树 你坐上车子试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 你的右手别放开轪盘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样用尽全力扭向任何一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也扭不过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 轪盘不要动 你下车来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己看看车轮转了多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全没有转动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经尽力扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话要如何转弯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没办法跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轪盘只是用来制造机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之就只能靠滑动后轮来过弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部的弯道都是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Drift可是拓海的强项
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的想象中的那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能完全Counter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.73,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,──────────────\N「Counter Steer」逆转轪盘。\NDrift中进入打滑状态时要往反\N方向打轪盘来保持行车路线。\N这里就是说反打轪盘时也不能够\N完全扭尽轪盘。\N────────{\fn黑体}{\i1}{\fs15}{\b1}{\fscx130}Initial D
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drift就会变得非常难以控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要稍微有一点Over Steer就一命呜呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.23,重叠对白,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(368,430)}「转向过度」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在入弯的时候出现Under Steer的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是相同命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这规则完全是让FF有利而订制的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是EG6吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FF的EG6的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用油门来抑制Over Steer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可以全速冲入弯道 用手刹来消除Under
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像86这样的FR要想不出意外跑完全程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在每个狭窄弧度又小的弯道以精确的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drift来控制转向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不应战是明智之举
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦了 被拓海听到这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他反而会想去出赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…店长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是健二前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池谷 关于上次那个脑袋坏掉的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经查过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该就是妙义Night Kids的庄司慎吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids的庄司慎吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说目前是NO.2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对Down Hill非常有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自称是Night Kids下坡最快的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了达到目的会不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其他队员眼中不太受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是和队长中里毅关系非常不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 所以才想挑战拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借此取得Night Kids的主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙对这次的事 已经放出了奇怪的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣言？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说Speed Stars胆怯 在逃避慎吾的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又不敢接受胶布Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 我们的颜面何存？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还真干得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他无论如何也要把拓海拉出来应战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我吗？不关我事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没打算要应战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是 就算怎么样被挑战也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没必要接受这种无理的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 和86比赛的事情怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时都OK 只是在等对方的回应而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把86的小鬼拉出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…看来会是一场有趣的比赛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾 你最近在搞些奇怪的小动作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么都是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不要把Night Kids的名声抹黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名声抹黑的是你这浑蛋才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被过时的86击败了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么地方的什么人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是拥有强劲马力的32
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败家之犬还能乱吠 到是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但别总只摆着一副领队的架子来说教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中里 你的面子我会帮你拾回的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾 你迟早也会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台86的可怕之处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎…毅先生也坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起Night Kids的领队是你才对 慎吾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 先把那台86送进解体场后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…我叫武内…我想找…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是佐代理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是树吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名公园兜风？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在上次的巴士站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点钟在那等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能从没有女朋友一族里脱出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情畅快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了 没什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车的技术真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…如果是拓海的话…可以哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事情 我非常在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还在洗车…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你躲在这里偷懒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不是…那个 稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真少见啊 树居然会看书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…啊…这是个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么…恋爱方程式？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生捕猎大法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…所以…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树会看这种书的话 那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次说的那个可爱的佐代理吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太狡猾了 不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是顺路经过所以买了 这本书我已经看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 就算问前辈你也不明白的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.55,0:13:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真敢说！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说中了也没办法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有这么方便的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们那个年代全部都要自己策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么…女生在第三次约会就会作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻要在一个浪漫的情况下进行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…我已经全部记得了 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事 上次和你说的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能给我放假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事吧 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.75,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭小鬼好让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定时刻到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理在哪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这呢 树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来要上次说胶布Death Match的答复
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好地传达给86的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 完全没有兴趣比赛 他是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可怎么行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来秋名的86是这么窝囊废的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是胶布Death Match就吓得要逃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他不愿意 我也有办法让他出赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们车手称呼转弯是叫攻弯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有点想考车牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考吧 我会教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 我会考虑一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.53,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名山…好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…女生对气氛很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻要在浪漫的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是绝佳的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛好沉重啊…伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EG6
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用防护杆来撞我…是在嫌我慢叫我让路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被咬住了 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能在佐代理前面出丑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要飞车了…一会就好 稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是车手间的胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会罢手的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…只要佐代理没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大件事了 树出意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是秋名山道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经被送进市立医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个马上去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩过火了 其实伤势没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一需要全面检查 所以要住几天医院
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代理呢？你们在一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她只是擦伤而已 已经回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了不让她受伤 拼命转过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子呢？85怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利做了Spin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要换一两件东西就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了 要保重身体喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了秋名湖以后 EG6就从背后出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EG6？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概没错 因为也是红色的EG6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入弯的时候突然从后面撞了我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个浑蛋 又来这一招
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要应战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match也好 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.37,0:22:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应战就应战！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓海！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要中他计啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布Death Match太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 拓海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的 无论什么样的比赛
